com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.validator.resolution.param
Interface IDeployResolutionObjectAttributeParameter

All Superinterfaces:
IDeployResolutionParameter
All Known Implementing Classes:
DeployResolutionObjectAttributeParameter
public interface IDeployResolutionObjectAttributeParameter
extends IDeployResolutionParameter

A resolution parameter that is linked to a deploy model object attribute.

Setting the resolution parameter has the effect of the resolution setting the underlying attribute in the object. The object must be contained in the topology of the resolution status object.
